snippet.title: Ekaki Official Trailer | Ashish Chanchlani | ACV Studios | Releasing on 27th November
snippet.description:
EKAKI is an original series that will be streaming on this channel for free (LOL haan haan 2025 Yehi saal aa raha hai)
Release Date  : 27th November 2025
Story batau? Ya khud dekhoge
Acha sunn lo synopsis :

7 friends..one weekend get away..an isolated village of maharashtra and a sinister force awaiting to feed on them.

snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

snippet.title: BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA INTERNATIONAL CUP 2025 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is finally over! The battleground ignites with the Official Trailer of BMIC 2025. 3 nations, #1 Crown, and no room for mercy. India, South Korea, and Japan are all set to collide in a battle for the ultimate supremacy. This isn't just competition; it's survival. The journey to glory begins now. Witness the chaos unfold on 31st Oct to 2nd Nov 2025. Catch it live only on the Krafton India Esports YouTube Channel.

snippet.title: Hind Ki Chadar | An Ode of Reverence & Sacrifice of Sri Guru Teg Bahadur Ji By Satinder Sartaaj
snippet.description:
#hindkichadar #gurutegbhadurji #satindersartaaj 

On The Sacred Occasion of THE 350th MARTYRDOM DAY of SRI GURU TEG BAHADUR JI, We're Presenting our Tribute "Hind Ki Chadar" | ‡®π‡®ø‡©∞‡®¶ ‡®ï‡©Ä ‡®ö‡®æ‡®¶‡®∞ | ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶ ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§ö‡§æ‡§¶‡§∞ By Satinder Sartaaj. 

The legacy of Guru Tegh Bahadur Ji, the Ninth Guru of the Sikhs, radiates as an unfading constellation of courage, sacrifice, and eternal truth. Revered as ‚ÄúHind Ki Chadar‚Äù ‚Äî the Sacred Shield of India, His supreme martyrdom did not belong to one faith alone, but became a benediction for all humanity ‚Äî safeguarding freedom of conscience, the sanctity of belief, and the dignity of the human spirit.

In this devotional offering, Dr. Satinder Sartaaj gathers the fragrance of centuries into verse, tracing the divine journey of the Guru ‚Äî from His serene birth in Guru-ke-Mahal to the transcendent moment in Delhi, where His luminous spirit embraced martyrdom and transformed Chandni Chowk into a sanctified ground of remembrance.
